************************************************************************************************************************
*****                                                               *****
*****                       Run Summary                             *****
*****                         EU-DEMO                               *****
*****            R=8.6m, A=2.8, Pfus= 1.6GW, Paux=50 MW               *****
*****         Nb3Sn TF Coils, He blanket coolant, ERCH              ***** 
